(Republished)

The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Henry McCoy, Appellant.

— Judgment, Supreme Court, Bronx County, rendered on February 1, 1978, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. The order of this court entered on May 24,1979 [70 AD2d 789] is vacated. Concur — Kupferman, J. P., Birns, Sullivan, Lupiano and Silverman, JJ.
